#~ "\"faqg_kru-forum\">&krusader; Forum</link>, or the krusader-users <ulink "
#~ "url=\"http://www.krusader.org/lists.php\">mailing lists</ulink>. For "
#~ "information on what remains to be done look at the <ulink url=\"http://"
#~ "www.krusader.org/phpBB/viewforum.php?f=10\">ToDo Forum</ulink>. Adding "
